com.interpss.dist

Interface DistBus

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Bus, BusRef<AcscBus>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAdaptable, IBusSwitchBreakModel, IDistBus, IDistBusAdaptation, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DistBusImpl

    public interface DistBus
extends Bus, IDistBus, IDistBusAdaptation, BusRef<AcscBus>
    A representation of the model object 'Dist Bus'. Dist Bus class for distribution analysis.

    The following features are supported:

    • Bus Code
    • Voltage Mag
    • VMag Unit
    • Voltage Ang
    • VAng Unit
    • Mva Rating3 P
    • Mva Rating1 P
    • Mva Rating Unit
    • XR3P
    • XR1P
    • Rated Voltage
    • Rated VUnit
    • Bus Rating
    • Bus Rating Unit
    • PFactor
    • Pf Unit
    • Eff
    • Motor Percent
    • Loading
    • Z1
    • Z0
    • Z2
    • ZUnit
    • Grounding
    • Load Schedule Data
    • Sc Point Bus Data
    See Also:
    DistPackage.getDistBus()
